  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ADD TO WISHLIST</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026100/extras/9d9b37be1384de8495408ed26bbe0576.poster.avif?t=1729344130\" width=736 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026100/extras/9d9b37be1384de8495408ed26bbe0576.webm?t=1729344130\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026100/extras/9d9b37be1384de8495408ed26bbe0576.mp4?t=1729344130\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>ESports Simulator is a simulation game where you can create and manage your own esports team. Control all aspects of a professional esports team - from selecting players, organizing training programs, building a gaming house, and purchasing equipment.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2></h2></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026100/extras/d8354462f16f193b4d37f1507a786439.avif?t=1729344130\" width=800 height=100 /></span> Create and manage your own esports team. Transfer players, develop training programs, and devise strategies to achieve the best performance.<br>{img}{STEAM_APP_IMAGE}/extras/PlayerBuyingGif.gif[/img]<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026100/extras/3d25be4e2e2a2bebeeae339c312ca05a.avif?t=1729344130\" width=800 height=100 /></span> Build and manage a dedicated gaming house for your team. Provide the best conditions to enhance your players' performance.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026100/extras/32d8cc7d363f8ea1b3b20faacd87ed1e.poster.avif?t=1729344130\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026100/extras/32d8cc7d363f8ea1b3b20faacd87ed1e.webm?t=1729344130\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026100/extras/32d8cc7d363f8ea1b3b20faacd87ed1e.mp4?t=1729344130\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026100/extras/2d681dba2a9fd9e48601987880ae4d8f.avif?t=1729344130\" width=800 height=100 /></span> Buy the best gaming equipment for your players. Observe and optimize the effects of different equipment on player performance.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026100/extras/8e8d6f431e494748bac9c3bdbbabfa04.poster.avif?t=1729344130\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026100/extras/8e8d6f431e494748bac9c3bdbbabfa04.webm?t=1729344130\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026100/extras/8e8d6f431e494748bac9c3bdbbabfa04.mp4?t=1729344130\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026100/extras/f77e476912fa5618ce26dd201409bbd8.avif?t=1729344130\" width=800 height=100 /></span> Test your team's performance in realistic simulated matches. Implement your strategies and compete against rival teams.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026100/extras/e498fc4992e5ae6f6650e6f170cab5e5.poster.avif?t=1729344130\" width=600 height=3